License:        MIT
License-File:   LICENSE
Author:         Serguey Zefirov <sergueyz@gmail.com>
Maintainer:     Serguey Zefirov <sergueyz@gmail.com>
Homepage:
Category:       Machine-learning
Build-Type:     Simple

Library
  Ghc-options:         -Wall
  Default-Language:    Haskell2010
  Build-Depends:       base               >=4.9 && <5
                     --
                     , mtl
                     , random
                     , vector
